20developing%20cultured%20pork%20that%20does%20not%20yet%20have%20approval%20in%20the%20US%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20would%20say%20it's%20a%20political%20decision%2C%20and%20politicians%20should%20basically%20not%20interfere%20with%20the%20food%20safety%20business%3B%20they%20should%20let%20the%20customers%20decide%20what%20they%20want%20to%20eat%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20USDA%20and%20FDA%20approve%20these%20kinds%20of%20foods%2C%20I%20would%20say%20this%20is%20the%20highest%20authority%20in%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20and%20their%20word%20should%20be%20followed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoliticians-dragging-lab-grown-cultured-meat-into-culture-wars-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713734264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661b42b41caec1275a6ff511%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoliticians-dragging-lab-grown-cultured-meat-into-culture-wars-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20industry%20of%20lab%20grown%20meat%20is%20still%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20but%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20politicians%20from%20trying%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20culture%20war%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoliticians-dragging-lab-grown-cultured-meat-into-culture-wars-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2219k%20kids%20in%20shelter%20homes%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20tops%20list%20with%201.5k%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713733559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109482329%2Cimgsize-1137646.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes