%20State%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Antony%20Blinken%20is%20expected%20to%20announce%20sanctions%20against%20the%20Netzah%20Yehuda%20battalion%20for%20alleged%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20the%20US%20has%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20an%20Israeli%20military%20unit.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20110727160330%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.ou.org%2Findex.php%2Fjewish_action%2Farticle%2F69714%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20battalion%20is%20composed%20of%20over%20900%20soldiers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20the%20possible%20sanctioning%20of%20the%20IDF%20unit%20came%20as%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20House%20of%20Representatives%20on%20Saturday%20passed%20a%20bill%20that%20includes%20more%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-house-democrats-republicans-vote-against-israel-gaza-aid-2024-4%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%2414%20billion%20in%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20well%20as%20%249%20billion%20in%20humanitarian%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eassistance%2C%20much%20of%20which%20will%20go%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unprecedented%20sanctions%20will%20prohibit%20the%20battalion%20and%20its%20members%20from%20receiving%20US%20military%20assistance%20or%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20imposed%20measures%20are%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2FPP410_INVEST_v2.1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1997%20Leahy%20vetting%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20forbids%20US%20foreign%20aid%20and%20Defense%20Department%20training%20programs%20from%20going%20to%20foreign%20security%2C%20military%2C%20and%20police%20units%20credibly%20alleged%20to%20have%20committed%20human%20rights%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20State%20Department%20req