20was%20standing%20at%20his%20normal%20batting%20position.%20Kohli%20was%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20third%20umpire's%20decision%20and%20RCB%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Faf%20Du%20Plessis%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F120301-faf-du-plessis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EFaf%20Du%20Plessis%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20controversial%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20crazy%2C%20rules%20are%20rules%2C%20Virat%20and%20myself%20thought%20that%20the%20ball%20was%20higher%20than%20the%20waist%20(on%20Kohli's%20dismissal)%2C%20I%20guess%20they%20measured%20from%20the%20popping%20crease%2C%20one%20team%20thinks%20it's%20high%2C%20the%20other%20doesn't.%20That's%20how%20the%20game%20goes%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Faf%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20the%20partnership%2C%20it%20was%20magnificent%20(on%20the%20Jacks-Patidar%20partnership)%2C%20but%20when%20you%20don't%20win%20too%20many%20games%2C%20some%20sort%20of%20panic%20sets%20in%20and%20the%20Narine%20over%20was%20game-changing.%20You%20don't%20feel%20that%20you%20have%20time%20to%20settle%20down%20and%20bat%20(on%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20IPL%20this%20season)%2C%20the%20game%20doesn't%20allow%20it%20to%20do%20that%2C%20obviously%20you%20have%20an%20extra%20batter%2C%20but%20in%20chases%20like%20these%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20match-up%20against%20Narine%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20the%20game%20changing%20over.%20The%20small%20things%2C%20I%20am%20actually%20proud%20of%20the%20boys%20tonight%2C%20the%20way%20we%20bowled%20and%20fielded%2C%20we%20did%20give%20away%20a%20couple%20of%20big%20overs%20towards%20the%20end%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20we%20kept%20them%20down%20to%20a%20par%20score.%20We%20thought%20we'll%20go%20hard%20in%20the%20batting%20powerplay%2C%20find%20those%20boundaries%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20innings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20desperate%2C%2010%2F10%20from%20an%20effort%20perspective%2C%20the%20way%20we%20put%20up%20the%20effort%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20faces%20told%20the%20story.%20We've%20got%20an%20unbelievable%20fanbase%2C%20we%20want%20to%20make%20them%20happy%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20have%20a%20smile%20on%20their%20face.%20We'll%20have%20to%20continue%20putting%20in%20our%20efforts%20and%20try%20to%20change%20things%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20remained%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20points%20table%20after%20suffering%20a%20one-run%20loss%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20KKR%20rode%20brilliant%20performances%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Phil%20Salt%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111341-philip-salt-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPhil%20Salt%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20score%20222%20before%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andre%20Russell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1536-andre-russell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndre%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20three%20wickets%20to%20clinch%20the%20victory%20for%20the%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713715080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F452e6eo_k_625x300_21_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fit-was-crazy-faf-du-plessis-blunt-take-on-virat-kohlis-controversial-dismissal-vs-kkr-5492100%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20was%20left%20furious%20following%20a%20controversial%20dismissal%20during%20the%20IPL%202024%20match%20between%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Warranty%20For%20Modi's%20Guarantee%26quot%3B%3A%20Revanth%20Reddy%20On%20Congress's%20Chances%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20his%20party%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%2014%20of%20the%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20December%202023%20after%20the%20Congress%20defeated%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20medicine%20has%20an%20expiry%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20told%20reporters%20in%20Karnataka's%20capital%20Bengaluru%20during%20an%20informal%20interaction%2C%20adding%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20lose%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20did%20not%20tell%20whether%20his%20confidence%20comes%20from%20the%20party%20winning%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20have%20been%20against%20the%20well-being%20and%20development%20of%20southern%20states%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20warranty%20for%20Modi's%20guarantees%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dared%20the%20Opposition%20BRS%20to%20win%20even%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20stand%20to%20gain%20from%20the%20votes%20that%20the%20BRS%20will%20lose%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20will%20still%20be%20able%20to%20take%20at%20least%2014%20seats%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20unlike%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20that%20have%20been%20discriminating%20against%20southern%20states%2C%20has%20always%20been%20inclusive%20by%20appointing%20leaders%20from%20these%20states%20to%20key%20cabinet%20and%20party%20positions%2C%20even%20when%20the%20Congress%20had%20swept%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Mr%20Reddy%20criticised%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20AIMIM%20of%20allegedly%20colluding%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20polarise%20voters%20during%20election%20season%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20in%20a%20city%20as%20Hyderabad%20where%20terror%20groups%20have%20tried%20to%20radicalise%20young%20Muslims%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20political%20party%20as%20AIMIM%20helped%20in%20containing%20radicalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20recently%20campaigned%20in%20Kerala%20too.%20He%20said%20the%20BJP%20will%20likely%20be%20restricted%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%2020%20among%20the%20130%20seats%20in%20the%20southern%20states.%20In%20the%20northern%20states%2C%20the%20BJP's%20numbers%20will%20decrease%20from%20what%20it%20had%20got%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20are%20being%20held%20in%20seven%20phases.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713714480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F61h4rtu_revanth-reddy_625x300_21_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-no-warranty-for-narendra-modis-guarantee-revanth-reddy-on-congresss-chances-in-telangana-5492231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20his%20party%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%2014%20of%20the%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-no-warranty-for-narendra-modis-guarantee-revanth-reddy-on-congresss-chances-in-telangana-5492231%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-no-warranty-for-narendra-modi