s%20will%20be%20absolutely%20repealed.%20Take%20it%20from%20me%2C%20I%20am%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20manifesto%20committee.%20I%20wrote%20every%20word%20of%20it%2C%20I%20know%20what%20the%20intention%20was.%20The%20CAA%20will%20be%20repealed%2C%20not%20amended.%20We%20have%20made%20it%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20will%20be%20repealed%20in%20the%20first%20session%20of%20Parliament%20in%20which%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc%20forms%20the%20government%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20claims%20of%20Mr%20Vijayan%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20opposed%20the%20Law%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20has%20spoken%20against%20the%20CAA%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20temple%20inauguration%20will%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%20he%20hopes%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAyodhya%20now%20has%20a%20temple.%20We%20are%20happy.%20People%20wanted%20the%20temple%20and%20a%20temple%20has%20come%20up.%20That%20should%20be%20the%20end%20of%20the%20story.%20Why%20should%20a%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20play%20a%20role%20in%20politics%20or%20in%20elections%20and%20on%20who%20should%20rule%20the%20country.%20It%20should%20have%20no%20role%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20criticised%20Mr%20Vijayan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20vocal%20these%20days%20against%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20Left%20leader%20to%20look%20at%20this%20election%20as%20a%20national%20election%2C%20which%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20its%20ally%20in%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%20was%20fighting%20this%20election%20in%20Kerala%20as%20if%20it%20is%20a%20state%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20from%20a%20national%20point%20of%20view%2C%20who%20is%20better%20placed%