sweet-for-words-see-post%2Farticleshow%2F109478799.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20nature-inspired%20tiny%20homes%20starting%20from%20%2458%2C000%20are%20now%20available%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20check%20them%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Madeiguincho%20tiny%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662195c120b15f0ff42965f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Madeiguincho%20tiny%20home.%3Cp%3EJo%C3%A3o%20Carranca%2FMadeiguincho%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Portugal-based%20carpentry%20company%20Madeiguincho%20began%20building%20tiny%20homes%20for%20European%20customers%20in%202016.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20eco-friendly%20designs%20are%20now%20for%20sale%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20first%20tiny%20home%20shipped%20to%20Queens%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETake%20a%20look%20inside%20a%20variety%20of%20their%20tiny%20homes%2C%20ranging%20from%20%2458%2C619%20to%20%2474%2C535%20in%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECraftsmanship%20runs%20in%20Gon%C3%A7alo%20Marrote's%20veins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20was%20a%20carpenter%2C%20and%20so%20was%20his%20father%20before%20him.%20In%201990%2C%20the%20Marrotes%20founded%20Madeiguincho%2C%20a%20Portugal-based%2C%20family-run%20woodworking%20company%20specializing%20in%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20his%20architectural%20education%20and%20inspired%20by%20his%20travels%20to%20places%20like%20Berlin%2C%20New%20York%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Nepal%2C%20Marrote%20steered%20the%20company%20toward%20a%20new%20frontier%20in%202016%3A%20tiny%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20would%20say%2C%20'Why%20would%20you%20change%20something%20that%20is%20already%20good%3F'%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20connected%20to%20my%20studies%20and%20my%20love%20for%20tiny%20houses%2C%26quot%3B%20Marrote%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20made%20one%2C%20people%20liked%20it%2C%20and%20then%20I%20made%20two%2C%20and%20the%20company%20started%20to%20grow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20company%20has%20built%2025%20tiny%20homes%2C%20with%20prices%20starting%20at%20%E2%82%AC55%2C000%20(about%20%2458%2C600).%20The%20homes%20vary%20in%20size%2C%20ranging%20from%2010%20meters%20(about%20108%20square%20feet)%2C%2012.5%20meters%20(about%20135%20square%20feet)%2C%20to%2017.5%20meters%20(about%20188%20square%20feet).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarrote%2C%20with%20a%20deep%20appreciation%20for%20nature%2C%20designs%20each%20custom-built%20home%20%E2%80%94%20no%20two%20are%20alike%20%E2%80%94%20to%20feel%20like%20an%20extension%20of%20its%20surrounding%20natural%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%2090%25%20of%20our%20product%20is%20sourced%20from%20wood%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20tiny%20homes%20are%20designed%20to%20make%20you%20feel%20at%20one%20with%20nature.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Madeiguincho%2C%20which%20constructs%20the%20tiny%20homes%20in%20Portugal%2C%20collaborating%20with%20local%20builders%20and%20architects%2C%20began%20shipping%20to%20the%20US.%20The%20first%20home%20landed%20in%20a%20Queens%2C%20New%20York%20backyard%2C%20where%20it%20is%20being%20used%20as%20an%20Airbnb%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20inside%20some%20of%20Madeiguincho's%20tiny%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20a%20home%20is%20purchased%20from%20Madeiguincho%20they%20pre-build%20on-site%20in%20their%20workshop%20in%20Portugal.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20carpenter%20working%20in%20the%20Madeiguincho%20workshop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622750f20b15f0ff4297e1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221255%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20carpenter%20working%20in%20the%20Madeiguincho%20workshop.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Madeiguincho%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHomes%20destined%20for%20the%20US%20are%20pre-assembled%20in%20Portugal%20before%20being%20transported%20in%20containers%20to%20their%20final%20destination.%20Once%20they%20arrive%20in%20the%20US%2C%20they%20are%20assembled%20on-site.%20The%20entire%20process%2C%20from%20transaction%20to%20delivery%2C%20typically%20takes%20about%2010%20months%2C%20according%20to%20Marrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeginning%20in%20early%202025%2C%20the%20company%20intends%20to%20divide%20the%20construction%20process%2C%20with%20half%20of%20the%20work%20carried%20out%20in%20Portugal%20and%20the%20other%20half%20completed%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMadeiguincho's%20tiny%20homes%20are%20eco-friendly%20and%20use%20sustainable%20construction%20methods.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224465%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Abano%20tiny%20home%20designed%20by%20Madeiguincho.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6621962e10c6b0cde5f0f60a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222977%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Abano%20tiny%20home%20designed%20by%20Madeiguincho.%3Cp%3EJo%C3%A3o%20Carranca%2FMadeiguincho%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Madeiguincho's%20tiny%20homes%20use%20well%20water%20systems%20and%20electricity%20from%20neighboring%20properties%2C%20while%20others%20are%20designed%20to%20operate%20independently%20from%20conventional%20utility%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20homes%2C%20in%20essence%2C%20operate%20off-grid%2C%20free%20from%20connections%20to%20public%20electrical%20grids%20or%20water%20mains.%20Instead%2C%20residents%20rely%20on%20sustainable%20methods%20like%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20and%20solar%20or%20battery-powered%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20an%20organism%20that%20doesn't%20need%20help%20to%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20Marrote%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMadeiguincho%2