Pankaj%20Tripathi's%20brother-in-law%20Rajesh%20Tiwari.%20The%20freak%20road%20accident%20has%20left%20his%20sister%20Sabita%20Tiwari%20with%20a%20fractured%20leg%20and%20jaw%20injury.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20around%204%3A30%20PM%2C%20officials%20confirmed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpankaj-tripathis-sister-stable-after-freak-road-accident-to-be-moved-to-kolkata-hospital%2Farticleshow%2F109478050.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Saved%20Another%20Leader%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Rajasthan%20Remark%20A%20Dig%20At%20Sonia%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20swipe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20cannot%20win%20elections%20have%20deserted%20the%20field%26quot%3B%20and%20become%20Rajya%20Sabha%20members%20from%20Rajasthan.%20This%20comes%20months%20after%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20was%20elected%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Upper%20House%20of%20Parliament%2C%20unopposed.%20Before%20her%20Rajya%20Sabha%20stint%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20has%20represented%20Congress%20stronghold%20Rae%20Bareli%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20two%20decades.%20She%20has%20also%20represented%20Amethi%20for%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jalore%20to%20campaign%20for%20BJP's%20Lumbaram%20Choudhary%2C%20who%20is%20taking%20on%20Congress's%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%20The%20Jalore%20constituency%20is%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%2C%20with%20the%20party%20winning%20it%20consistently%20for%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20rally%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20questioned%20if%20Congress%20MPs%20representing%20Rajasthan%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20raised%20the%20state's%20issues.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20sent%20a%20South%20leader%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Rajasthan.%20Has%20he%20never%20spoken%20about%20Rajasthan%3F%20No.%20You%20also%20sent%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20was%20unwell%2C%20but%20did%20you%20see%20him%20in%20Rajasthan%3F%20And%20now%2C%20you%20have%20saved%20another%20leader.%20Those%20who%20cannot%20fight%20elections%2C%20win%20elections%20have%20deserted%20the%20field%20and%20come%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Mrs%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20six%20Congress%20MPs%20represent%20Rajasthan%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20--%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Neeraj%20Dangi%2C%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%2C%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20Pramod%20Tiwari%20and%20Mukul%20Wasnik%3B%20only%20Mr%20Dangi%20is%20actually%20from%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20had%20%26quot%3Bpunished%26quot%3B%20Congress%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Twelve%20out%20of%2025%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20had%20voted%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20last%20Friday.%20The%20remaining%20will%20vote%20this%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajasthan%20is%20seeped%20in%20patriotism.%20It%20knows%20that%20Congress%20can%20never%20make%20a%20strong%20India.%20The%20country%20does%20not%20want%20such%20a%20Congress%20government.%20The%20country%20does%20not%20want%20the%20pre-2014%20situation%20to%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20Opposition%20party%20with%20his%20oft-repeated%20%26quot%3Bremote%20control%26quot%3B%20barb%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20respected%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20government%20was%20run%20by%20remote%20control.%26quot%3B%20The%20barb%20is%20a%20standard%20line%20of%20attack%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20which%20it%20claims%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20de%20facto%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20took%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20the%202013%20episode%20in%20which%20he%20had%20said%20a%20UPA%20government%20ordinance%20to%20shield%20convicted%20lawmakers%20from%20disqualification%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Btorn%20up%20and%20thrown%20away%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20imagine%2C%20a%20cabinet%20note%20is%20torn%20up%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20by%20a%20ruling%20party%20leader.%20Can%20such%20a%20weak%20dispensation%20make%20the%20country%20strong%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20asked%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20responsible%20for%20its%20current%20situation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20that%20once%20won%20400%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20seats%20cannot%20even%20contest%20300%20seats%20now.%20They%20are%20not%20getting%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713703800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fteinq52o_modi-sonia-split_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-sonia-gandhi-those-who-cant-win-elections-pms-rajya-sabha-swipe-at-sonia-gandhi-5490639%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20apparent%20swipe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20cannot%20win%20elections%20have%20deserted%20the%20field%26quot%3B%20and%20become%20Rajya%20Sabha%20members%20from%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-sonia-gandhi-those-who-cant-win-elections-pms-rajya-sabha-swipe-at-sonia-gandhi-5490639%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-so