e%20was%20extreme%20heat%20inside%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20was%20feeling%20unwell%20and%20parched%20before%20the%20morning%20broadcast%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20keep%20a%20water%20bottle%20with%20me.%20Be%20it%20a%20fifteen-minute%20or%20half%20an%20hour%20broadcast%2C%20I%20have%20never%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20sip%20water%20during%20broadcasts%20in%20my%2021%20years%20of%20career.%20But%2C%20I%20felt%20parched%20even%20as%2015%20minutes%20were%20left%20for%20the%20broadcast%20to%20end.%20When%20the%20TV%20was%20showing%20visuals%20and%20not%20my%20face%2C%20I%20pointed%20to%20the%20floor%20manager%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20Bangla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Flopamudra.sinha.14%252Fvideos%252F625766379751908%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sinha%20further%20said%20that%20she%20wasn't%20getting%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20some%20water%20because%20only%20general%20stories%20were%20running%20without%20any%20bytes.%20%26quot%3BTowards%20the%20end%20(of%20the%20bulletin)%2C%20a%20byte%20came%20and%20I%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20drink%20some%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20drinking%20the%20water%2C%20she%20somehow%20completed%20two%20stories%20while%20two%20others%20were%20still%20pending%20when%20she%20fainted%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20reading%20a%20heatwave%20story%2C%20my%20speech%20started%20getting%20slurred.%20I%20tried%20to%20complete%20my%20presentation.%20The%20teleprompter%20faded%20away%20and%20I%20blacked%20out.%20But%20luckily%2C%20it%20happened%20while%20a%2030%20to%2040%20seconds%20animation%20was%20playing%20out%20on%20television.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20I%20collapsed%20on%20my%20chair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrinking%20enough%20fluids%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20you%20can%20do%20to%20prevent%20heat%20illness%2C%20even%20when%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20men%20were%20seen%20rushing%20to%20her%20aid%20as%20she%20fainted%20and%20splashed%20water%20on%20her%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sinha%20also%20apologised%20to%20her%20channel%20for%20the%20mishap%20and%20also%20thanked%20the%20producers%20for%20managing%20the%20broadcast%20after%20she%20fainted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20even%20dreamt%20that%20something%20like%20this%20would%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20advised%20the%20viewers%20to%20take%20care%20of%20themselves%20amid%20the%20scorching%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20heatwave%20affecting%20parts%20of%20Odisha%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%20is%20the%20second%20heatwave%20spell%20this%20month.%20The%20first%20spell%20scorched%20parts%20of%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20maximum%20temperatures%20at%20some%20places%20were%20recorded%20seven%20to%20eight%20degrees%20above%20normal.%20Midnapore%20and%20Bankura%20in%20West%20Bengal%20recorded%2044.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%2044.6%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threshold%20for%20a%20heatwave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%20A%20severe%20heatwave%20is%20declared%20if%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20temperature%20exceeds%206.4%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713699180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2