nt%20of%20rice%20imported%20from%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Frussia-warns-pakistan-of-banning-rice-imports-over-phytosanitary-concerns%2Farticleshow%2F109477207.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Frussia-warns-pakistan-of-banning-rice-imports-over-phytosanitary-concerns%2Famp_articleshow%2F109477207.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Frussia-warns-pakistan-of-banning-rice-imports-over-phytosanitary-concerns%2Famp_articleshow%2F109477207.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22P%20Chidambaram's%20Big%20Poll%20Promise%3A%20Law%20To%20Enforce%20'Bail%20Is%20Rule'%20Principle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Union%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20said%20today%20that%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20it%20would%20enact%20a%20special%20law%20to%20bring%20into%20effect%20the%20legal%20principle%20established%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20%26quot%3Bbail%20is%20the%20rule%2C%20and%20jail%20is%20the%20exception%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20promising%20to%20bring%20a%20special%20law%20that%20would%20say%2C%20'Bail%20is%20the%20rule%2C%20jail%20is%20the%20exception'.%20it%20was%20a%20great%20son%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Justice%20Krishna%20who%20emphasised%20this%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20rule%20is%20rarely%20followed%20in%20the%20lower%20judiciary%2C%20magistrates%2C%20and%20district%20judges%2C%20ultimately%2C%20not%20everybody%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20get%20bail.%2065%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20prisoners%20are%20under%20trial%3B%20they%20are%20not%20convicts%2C%20so%20why%20are%20they%20in%20jail%3F%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20undertrials%20are%20OBCs%2C%20SC%20and%20STs%3B%20therefore%2C%20we%20would%20bring%20a%20special%20law%3A%20'Bail%20is%20the%20rule%2C%20jail%20is%20the%20exception'%20--%20everybody%20after%20the%20first%2015%20days%20of%20interrogation%20by%20police%20or%20the%20CBI%20must%20be%20granted%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%20also%20said%20that%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20it%20will%20repeal%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20the%20three%20criminal%20laws%20brought%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20repeal%2C%20amend%20and%20review%20the%20following%20sets%20of%20laws%20-%20CAA%202019%20is%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list.%20The%20Farmers%20Produce%2C%20Trade%20and%20Commerce%20Promotion%20of%20Facilitation%20Act%202020%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20(Second)%20Sanhita%20that%20is%20equivalent%20to%20the%20IPC%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20that%20is%20the%20CrPC%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20(Second)%20Act%20that%20is%20the%20Evidence%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20by%20ANI%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20five%20will%20be%20totally%20repealed.%20Then%20we%20have%20eight%20laws%20that%20will%20be%20repealed%20and%20new%20laws%20will%20be%20made.%20Then%20we%20have%2025%20laws%2C%20which%20will%20be%20amended%20and%20brought%20on%20par%20with%20the%20Constitution.%20So%20we%20are%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20will%20be%20repealed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20from%202008%20till%202012%20under%20the%20UPA%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20rejected%20the%20CPM%20leaders'%20allegation%20that%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20were%20silent%20on%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShashi%20Tharoor%20has%20widely%20spoken%20against%20the%20CAA%20and%20it%20was%20widely%20reported.%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20said%20we%20oppose%20CAA%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20committee%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20in%20an%20election%20rally%2C%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20had%20alleged%20that%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20were%20silent%20on%20CAA%2C%20showing%20the%20%26quot%3Bsame%20mindset%26quot%3B%20as%20Sangh%20Parivar.%20He%20further%20alleged%20that%20Kerala%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20initially%20joined%20the%20Left%20front%20to%20oppose%20the%20CAA%2C%20withdrew%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20its%20national%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%20for%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20under%20the%20section%2C%20%26quot%3BREVERSING%20THE%20DAMAGE%26quot%3B%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20promise%20that%20all%20anti-people%20laws%20passed%20by%20the%20BJP%2FNDA%20without%20proper%20parliamentary%20scrutiny%20and%20debate%2C%20especially%20those%20relating%20to%20workers%2C%20farmers%2C%20criminal%20justice%2C%20environment%20and%20forests%20and%20digital%20data%20protection%2C%20will%20be%20thoroughly%20reviewed%20and%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20enables%20citizenship%20to%20undocumented%20migrants%20belonging%20to%20six%20non-Muslim%20communities%20--%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20and%20Christian%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%20who%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%20and%20reduces%20the%20period%20to%20qualify%20for%20citizenship%20from%20existing%2011%20years%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713698700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F6fab26sk_p-chidambaram-ani_625x300_10_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sab