%3EHowever%2C%20with%20no%20investment%2C%20the%20two%20young%20entrepreneurs%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20meet%20requirements.%20Their%20margins%20too%20were%20low%20as%20they%20were%20purchasing%20the%20books%20from%20the%20shopkeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20second-hand%20sellers%20buy%20these%20books%20from%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwalas%20(scrap%20collectors%20and%20sellers)%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20a%20weight%20basis%2C%20which%20gives%20them%20huge%20margins.%20We%20first%20had%20to%20build%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20purchase%20the%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20started%20visiting%20scrap%20sellers%20in%20Muzaffarpur%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344538%2Fhow-to-read-books-for-competitive-exams-iit-gate-upsc-ifs-officer-himanshu-tyagi-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuying%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20dynamic%20duo%20boasts%20partnerships%20with%20nearly%20every%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20city%2C%20with%20their%20network%20now%20reaching%20into%20Patna%20and%20other%20regions%20of%20Bihar.%20Leveraging%20the%20power%20of%20word-of-mouth%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20Instagram%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20successfully%20moved%20over%206%2C000%20books%2C%20raking%20in%20sales%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20truly%20sets%20them%20apart%20is%20their%20unwavering%20determination%20to%20thrive%20and%20establish%20a%20distinctive%20identity.%20Starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20they%20nurtured%20this%20enterprise%20from%20the%20confines%20of%20their%20own%20home%20while%20juggling%20college%20commitments%20by%20day.%20Their%20nights%20are%20dedicated%20to%20fielding%20calls%2C%20managing%20messages%2C%20overseeing%20shipping%20logistics%2C%20handling%2