physical%2C%20through%20our%20sales%20officers%20on%20ground.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20blended%20tech%20model%20with%20a%20physical%20branch%20network%20where%20most%20of%20the%20underwriting%20and%20collections%20are%20done%20online%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20social%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%2020%20percent%20of%20their%20monthly%20disbursements%20go%20to%20existing%20customers%2C%20helping%20them%20grow%20their%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20clients%2C%20Divya%20explains%20how%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20policy%20helped%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20runs%20a%20company%20called%20Brookwoods%20Technologies%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20loan%20for%20her%20business.%20Since%20her%20business%20was%20less%20than%20a%20year%20old%2C%20most%20lenders%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20NBFCs%20and%20banks%20lend%20after%20a%20business%20completes%20three%20years%20of%20operations.%20Kinara%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20such%20conditions%20and%20gave%20us%20a%20loan%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20immensely.%20The%20entire%20process%20was%20streamlined%20and%20online.%20An%20officer%20from%20their%20team%20came%20for%20inspection%20and%20sanctioned%20the%20loan%20very%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivya%20has%20been%20able%20to%20grow%20her%20company%20to%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores%20in%203%20years.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20all%20this%2C%20Hardika%20states%20that%20Kinara%20is%20profitable%20today%20and%20rearing%20to%20reach%20more%20business%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20existence%20began%20thanks%20to%20a%20woman%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20hence%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20their%20HerVikas%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20discounts%20to%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20boost%20their%20businesses%2C%20remains%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20d